## Introduction
This software is used to identify candidate genes.
Here, we demonstrate the identification of the SCPLâ… A gene in Tieguanyin as an example, 
based on parameter thresholds for gene filtering.


## Install
### Preparation before use
Please ensure that you have installed BLAST and Hmmer software correctly before use.
You can execute the following two commands to test the software installation situation.

```shell
# Test blastp
blastp -version
# Test Hmmsearch
hmmsearch -h
```
### Environment
python >= 3.5

### Install Gfanno
There are several ways to run gfanno
- Installing using pypi
```shell
pip install gfanno
```
- Installing using source code
```shell
git clone https://github.com/qunjie-zhang/tea_flavonoid.git
cd tea_flavonoid
python setup.py install
```
- Run directly without installation
```shell
git clone https://github.com/qunjie-zhang/tea_flavonoid.git
cd tea_flavonoid
python -m gfanno
```

## Usage
Use it as a terminal command. For all parameters, type `gfanno -h`.
```shell
usage: gfanno [-h] -f FASTA -s SEED --hmm HMM [-o OUTPUT] [--domain DOMAIN]
              [--identity IDENTITY] [--blastp_qcovhsp BLASTP_QCOVHSP]
              [--pfam_coverage PFAM_COVERAGE] [--DEBUG DEBUG]

options:
  -h, --help               show this help message and exit
  -f FASTA, --fasta FASTA  input fasta file path
  -s SEED, --seed SEED     input seed file path
  --hmm HMM                Input files required the hmmsearch results file
  -o OUTPUT, --output      output file path (Default:Result.txt)
  --domain DOMAIN          The name(s) of the matching structural domain(s)
                           should be entered;(Default:Peptidase_S10)
  --identity IDENTITY      Entering the threshold value for blastp
                           identityfunction: Filter out sequences that are
                           smaller than the identity threshold. (Default:90)
  --blastp_qcovhsp         BLASTP_QCOVHSP
                           Entering the threshold value for the Query Coverage
                           Per Subject of Blastp.(Default:80)
  --pfam_coverage          PFAM_COVERAGE
                           Entering the threshold value for the Coverage of
                           Hmmsearch. (Default:50)

``` 
## Dataset
You can download the sample dataset included in this software, which includes seed files and hmm models
[Seed File](https://github.com/interestingcn/gfanno_test/releases/download/Dataset/seed.zip)
[Hmm File](https://github.com/interestingcn/gfanno_test/releases/download/Dataset/hmm.zip)

